    <p class="hero-subtitle">Chowk Bazar · Chittagong · Bangladesh</p>
    <p class="hero-desc">A sacred shrine commemorating the blessed visit of <strong style="color:var(--gold-light)">Guru Nanak Dev Ji</strong> in 1507–08. One of the oldest Sikh holy places in Bengal, standing as a beacon of faith, brotherhood, and universal love for over five centuries.</p>
